  "title": "A round white UFO spotted in Bela Vista-SP [1999]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/15/a-round-white-ufo-spotted-in-sao-paulo-sp-1999/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-u9",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>DEC 16th, 1999</strong>. Time: 03h50 am. Duration: 20 minutes. Two witnesses in the city of Bela Vista, State of São Paulo, spotted a round white UFO with red and green edges. The objetc was &#8220;bigger than a big plane&#8221;, and also round in shape but with part of its body in a triangular form. The two observers were using binoculars and saw the UFO about 5 km away from them, in favorable weather conditions for sky observation.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.566. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Avistamento de objeto voador não identificado em Bela Vista, São Paulo”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>DEC 16th, 1999. Time: 03h50 am. Duration: 20 minutes. Two witnesses in the city of Bela Vista, State of São Paulo, spotted a round white UFO with red and green edges. The objetc was &#8220;bigger than a big plane&#8221;, and also round in shape but with part of its body in a triangular form. The [&hellip;]</p>\n",
